<plot>The film is dedicated to the 80th anniversary of the painter Lily Vermut. She is the first artist, who made a one-women independent textile exhibition in Bulgaria in 1963. Surrounded by her books, the old clock, and her art works, she tells the story of the past, the present, and discusses the meaning of art.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?126900</url></doc>
